txt.en: 'A live one, eh? I thought the Orcs cleaned this place out.'
'You should run away, little creature, if you value your hide....'
'...But I won't let you do no such thing!'
'Kill the little worm! Our friend will not like to see it underfoot.'
'Where is the Thane? Where is Aldstan?'
'I am here for you, Aldstan! I am hunting you.'
